- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper deals with incorporating visual features in the translation model.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of self-attentive networks and auxiliary objectives in the model.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with a task that involves both language and vision, which are important areas of AI research.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with multimodal translation, which involves both text and images.
